TO HELP SOMEBODY ♪

00:24.676 --> 00:27.940
♪ WHEN THE EDGE OF
SURRENDER'S IN SIGHT ♪

00:28.115 --> 00:30.682
♪ DON'T YOU WORRY ♪

00:30.856 --> 00:33.685
♪ IT'S GONNA BE ALL RIGHT ♪

00:37.254 --> 00:38.777
♪ 'CAUSE I'M ALWAYS READY ♪

